Acceptance: Implement Issue creation and Issue/PR close/reopen through the shared preview-confirm-apply framework. Resolved targets, revisions, authority, success, denial, replay, stale state, provider failure, idempotent retry, receipts, and no-duplicate webhook reconciliation are independently tested. Keep the action family disabled unless the explicit P19 pilot gate or the completed P21 attribution rollout permits it. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-12-github-item-room-routing.md.